cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use simval in your research, please cite it as below."
title: "simval — deterministic verification + reference-oracle for computational physics"
abstract: >-
  A local-first, LLM-free verification layer and reference-oracle for computational
  physics simulations (molecular dynamics, N-body, waves, fluids, electromagnetism,
  quantum). Provides deterministic diagnostics, provenance manifests, and an oracle
  that validates candidate simulations against canonical reference cases across domains.
